org.perfcake.message.generator

Class ConstantSpeedMessageGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.perfcake.message.generator.AbstractMessageGenerator
      • org.perfcake.message.generator.DefaultMessageGenerator
        • org.perfcake.message.generator.ConstantSpeedMessageGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessageGenerator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CustomProfileGenerator

    public class ConstantSpeedMessageGenerator
extends DefaultMessageGenerator
    A generator that tries to achieve given speed of messages per second. Uses the underlying buffer of SenderTasks in DefaultMessageGenerator. This buffer smoothens the changes in the speed. If you need the generator to change its speed more aggressively, configure DefaultMessageGenerator.setSenderTaskQueueSize(int).
    Author:
    Martin Večeřa
